3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20failed%20to%20get%20into%20Google%205%20times.%20The%201st%20time%20was%20in%202018.%20I%20received%20an%20online%20assessment%20from%20Google.%20I%20was%20excited%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20pass%20the%20OA.%20Afterwards%2C%20an%20interviewer%20reached%20out%20to%20me.%20They%20had%20reviewed%20my%20OA%20answers%20and%20wanted%20to%20give%20me%20a%20second%20chance.%20Unfortunately%2C%20I%20didn't%20pass%20on%20this%20attempt%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20her%20other%20attempts%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%203rd%20attempt%20was%20in%20early%202020.%20I%20had%20a%20phone%20screening%20interview%2C%20which%20I%20didn't%20pass.%20Persisting%2C%20I%20applied%20again%20in%202020%20for%20a%20Site%20Reliability%20Engineer%20role.%20After%20four%20rounds%20of%20interviews%20and%20receiving%20positive%20feedback%2C%20the%20role%20was%20unfortunately%20canceled%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7190731501188050944%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22935%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Wang%20said%20that%20finally%2C%20on%20her%20fifth%20attempt%2C%20she%20passed%20the%20interview%20and%20received%20a%20gift%20from%20the%20tech%20giant.%20%26quot%3BIn%202022%2C%20on%20my%205th%20attempt%2C%20I%20finally%20secured%20a%20Software%20Engineer%20role.%20After%20passing%20the%20interview%2C%20I%20received%20a%20gift%20from%20Google%20along%20with%20a%20paper%20that%20said%2C%20'Congratulations%2C%20searching%20for%20a%20job%20is%20hard...'%20I've%20kept%20this%20paper%20for%202%20years%20now%20as%20it%20continually%20reminds%20me%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20persistence%20and%20not%20giving%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%20said%20that%20the%