0with%20a%202024%20Subaru%20Ascent%20Touring%2C%20dressed%20in%20an%20eye-catching%20Dark%20Mahogany%20Pearl%20paint%20job%2C%20to%20see%20if%20it%20can%20still%20compete%20against%20the%20latest%20from%20Honda%20and%20Toyota.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20SUV%20to%20be%20a%20well-made%20and%20capable%20family%20hauler%20with%20a%20great%20all-wheel-drive%20system%20and%20comfortable%20cabin%2C%20but%20its%20new%20tech%20and%20the%20overall%20driving%20experience%20still%20need%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Ascent's%20arrival%20in%20late%202018%20was%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20Subaru.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subaru%20Ascent%200386%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ba5610d4e353ee7228b456a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202019%20Subaru%20Ascent%20Touring%20we%20drove%20back%20in%202018.%20%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FJessica%20Tyler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Subaru%20loyalists%2C%20the%20Ascent%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20godsend.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20Forester%20and%20Outback%20owners%20could%20upgrade%20to%20a%20larger%2C%20three-row%20SUV%20from%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubaru's%20previous%20attempt%20at%20a%20family%20SUV%2C%20the%20B9%20Tribeca%2C%20failed%20to%20garner%20any%20real%20consideration%20from%20most%20buyers%20due%20to%20its%20small%20size%2C%20poor%20performance%2C%20and%20oddball%20styling.%20Subaru%20reigned%20in%20the%20Tribeca's%20weird%20looks%20and%20gave%20it%20more%20power%20in%202008.%20Unfortunately%2C%20those%20efforts%20failed%20to%20generate%20market%20traction%20and%20Subaru%20eventually%20gave%20up%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20slew%20of%20new%20rivals%20hit%20the%20market%20in%20the%20years%20after%20Ascent's%20debut.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221823%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%202023%20Toyota%20Highlander.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fbb220dfb1341e90041b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221216%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202023%20Toyota%20Highlander.%3Cp%3EToyota%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EToyota%20introduced%20an%20all-new%204th%20generation%20Highlander%20in%20late%202019.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20Hyundai%20introduced%20the%20Palisade%20while%20Kia%20launched%20the%20Telluride.%20The%20Korean%20sisters%20have%20garnered%20both%20sales%20and%20critical%20acclaim.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Nissan%20rolled%20out%20their%20long-awaited%205th%20generation%20Pathfinder%20while%20Honda%20followed%20suit%20with%20the%20new%204th%20generation%20Pilot%20in%20late%202022.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%202024%20Subaru%20Ascent%20is%20available%20in%208%20different%20trim%20levels.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223068%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subaru%20Ascent%20front%20end%20with%20large%20back%20grille%2C%20large%20chrome%20bar%2C%20and%20LED%20headlights%20that%20turn%20with%20the%20steering%20wheel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fc58710dfcda409647cea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222301%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Subaru%20Ascent's%20new%20updated%20looks.%20%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20base%202024%20Subaru%20Ascent%20starts%20at%20%2434%2C195%20in%20the%20US%2C%20while%20our%20top-spec%20Ascent%20Touring%20test%20car%20starts%20at%20%2448%2C495.%20With%20fees%2C%20our%20test%20car%20carried%20an%20as-tested%20price%20of%20%2449%2C931.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20revised%20front%20facia%20leads%20the%20Acsent's%20mid-cycle%20updates.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ascent's%20front%20end%20features%20a%20large%20blacked%20grille%20with%20a%20prominent%20chrome%20bar%20and%20Subaru%20logo%20protruding%20out.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20s