ns%20of%20the%20power%20of%20a%20project%20of%20this%20scope.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20of%20their%20most%20recent%20projects%20is%20empowering%20the%20rickshaw%20community%20in%20Matheran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENot%20a%20crowdfunding%20campaign%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Matheran%20e-Auto%20Rickshaw%20Fund%E2%80%99%20lets%20you%20invest%20in%20hand-rickshaw-pullers%20in%20Matheran%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20upgrade%20to%20e-rickshaws%20and%20earn%20higher%20incomes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20credit%20will%20ensure%20them%20a%20life%20away%20from%20the%20drudgery%20and%20hard%20work%20of%20pulling%20rickshaws%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20on%20the%20mud%20roads%20of%20Matheran.%20The%20money%20will%20be%20channelled%20towards%20them%20buying%20e-rickshaws%20and%20your%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336102%2Fpimpri-chinchwad-maharashtra-wins-medal-for-urban-innovation-by-ias-shekhar-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ram%20says%2C%20can%20enable%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20per%20month%20for%20these%20hand-rickshaw-pullers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20project%20will%20ensure%20that%20these%20handrickshaw%20pullers%20will%20get%20the%20funds%20to%20buy%20e-rickshaws%20which%20will%20help%20ease%20their%20task%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fmatheran-1-1714466651-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348643%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20project%20will%20ensure%20that%20these%20handrickshaw%20pullers%20will%20get%20the%20funds%20to%20buy%20e-rickshaws%20which%20will%20help%20ease%20their%20task%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sunil%20Shinde%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20how%20does%20this%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20an%20individual%20invests%20in%20a%20certain%20project%20on%20our%20platform%2C%20the%20money%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20investee%20via%20a%20regulated%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ram%20explains.%20He%20adds%20that%20Rang%20De%20is%20regulated%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20has%20their%20NBFC-P2P%20(Non-Banking%20Financial%20Company)%20licence%20in%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20allows%20any%20Indian%20to%20lend%20money%20to%20a%20fellow%20Indian%20over%20the%20internet%20through%20our%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20money%20is%20invested%2C%20a%20lot%20ensues%20behind%20the%20scenes%20for%20the%20funds%20to%20meet%20its%20purpose.%20In%20this%20particular%20project%2C%20Rang%20De%20has%20partnered%20with%20Tisser%20%E2%80%94%20a%20not-for-profit%20trust%20that%20is%20providing%20sustainable%20livelihoods%2C%20income%20opportunities%2C%20and%20access%20to%20professional%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erural%20craftspersons%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20through%20professional%20training%2C%20innovative%20models%2C%20and%20technological%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETisser%20identifies%20the%20rickshaw-pullers%20who%20wish%20to%20upgrade%20to%20e-rickshaws%2C%20helps%20them%20with%20finances%20(they%20have%20raised%20over%20Rs%2014%2C00%2C000)%20and%20ensures%20that%20these%20rickshaw-pullers%20repay%20the%20loan%20with%20interest%20every%20month%20over%2030%20months.%20Ram%20adds%20that%20another%20supporting%20arm%20of%20the%20project%20is%20Caring%20Friends%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Mumbai-based%20philanthropic%20group%20that%20acts%20as%20a%20bridge%20between%20NGOs%20and%20donors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20each%20of%20these%20is%20crucial.%20As%20Ram%20sees%20it%2C%20championing%20a%20micro-credit%20system%20is%20vital%20now%20more%20than%20ever.%20%E2%80%9COnly%2012.8%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20eligible%20population%20has%20access%20to%20formal%20credit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ram%20highlights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMaking%20loans%20accessible%20to%20a%20credit-starved%20country%20is%20what%20we%20started%20out%20intending%20to%20do.%20Through%20the%20years%20a%20steadfast%20focus%20on%20this%20social%20mission%20coupled%20with%20us%20staying%20our%20course%2C%20has%20built%20trust%20in%20our%20social%20investors.%E2%80%9D%20And%20what%E2%80%99s%20amazing%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317213%2Fhow-to-apply-isb-accelerator-programme-for-social-impact-startups%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20witness%20impact%20at%20scale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImagine!%20A%20person%20living%20in%20Mumbai%20can%20invest%20in%20someone%20who%20is%20in%20Matheran.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20is%20that%20the%20RBI%20gives%20the%20person%20who%20is%20borrowing%20money%20the%20same%20status%20as%20he%20would%20get%20if%20he%20were%20borrowing%20from%20a%20bank.%20He%20will%20get%20a%20credit%20score%20in%20all%20the%20four%20credit%20bureaus%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20clarifies%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20how%20the%20Matheran%20project%20strikes%20a%20chord%20in%20him%2C%20Ram%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20liberating%20to%20know%20that%20a%20practice%20(hand-pulled%20rickshaws)%20that%20has%20been%20in%20existence%20since%20the%20British%20era%20will%20be%20put%20to%20an%20end.%E2%80%9D%20He%20sees%20this%20as%20a%20classic%20textbook%20example%20of%20blending%20many%20social%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20engaging%20communities%2C%20protecting%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318643%2Fengineer-helps-mir-nomadic-community-gujarat-sell-traditional-beadwork-tokar-designs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreating%20dignified%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20into%20one.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20road%20Rang%20De%20is%20traversing%2C%20Ram%20says%20it%20is%20a%20long%20one.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20impact%20a%20million%20social%20investors%20and%20households%20that%20the%20investment%20is%20helping.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Shinde%20who%20now%20watches%20with%20happiness%20as%20his%20friend%20drives%20an%20e-rickshaw%2C%20feels%20proud.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy%20I%20could%20do%20my%20bit%20for%20the%20locals%20of%20Matheran%2C%20who%20take%20great%20pride%20in%20their%20work.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvest%20in%20an%20e-rickshaw%20and%20help%20hand%20rickshaw%20pullers%20today!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frangde.in%2Ffund%2Fmatheranerickshawfund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInvest%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frangde.in%2Ffund%2F